Comment: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:22.29,RAINBOW INSERT,,0000,0000,0000,,When you can't sleep at night, you begin to hear the rain making music.
Comment: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:38.42,RAINBOW INSERT,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a gentle ride on the clouds.  Let's sail toward the future.
Comment: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:55.17,RAINBOW INSERT,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, a bridge spans the starless, dark sky.
Comment: 0,0:18:56.32,0:19:12.92,RAINBOW INSERT,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that on these rainy days, you can catch a glimpse of the seven-colored illusion.
Comment: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:28.54,RAINBOW INSERT,,0000,0000,0000,,Something unthinkable may happen on the trail, but simply cast it off to the side as a bad dream,
Comment: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:44.09,RAINBOW INSERT,,0000,0000,0000,,so that the more we walk forward, the more we are graced with light.
Comment: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:51.67,RAINBOW INSERT,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear my rainbow.
