Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:41.16,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}my life for those\Nwhom I must protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:45.50,RAINBOW ED EN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Even if I rot away...
